data.description: Gorgeous 3/2 home with split bedroom floorplan with tons of upgrades that is better than new!  Meticulously maintained inside and out, this home boasts 9 foot ceilings with crown molding throughout complimented by the vaulted ceiling in the bright and airy great room.  The beautiful and inviting kitchen area features custom cabinets, granite countertops, tile backsplash and walk in pantry!  The spacious master suite features a trey ceiling, customer tiled shower, double vanity with granite top and a walk in closet.  The secondary bedrooms offer plenty of closet and storage space.  Stepping out the back door you will find a roomy screened in porch that overlooks the very spacious back yard with an impressive 25x24 detached garage aka "man cave deluxe" surrounded by PVC privacy fencing !  Amenities include:  sprinklers in ALL areas of lawn (with separate meter), gutters all around house than drain into the lawn area and not next to house, extra concrete drive poured to detached garage, flood lights at all corners of house, large security light in front yard and the list goes on!  Home is termite bonded and internet is provided via AT&T Fiber Optic. Words do not do this home justice. This is a MUST SEE! Virtual Tour- https://youtu.be/QdHn9HvqxDw
